***nrf24L01 Pin Connection

VCC  -> 3.3V
GND  -> GND
CS   -> D9
CE   -> D10
MOSI -> 11
SCK  -> 13
MISO -> 12

#Use 10uF 25V cap (Between to Nrf VCC and GND Pins)


***Current Sensor
#See pic. "Current Sensor Connection"

2x10kohm Res.(voltage divider 5V To 2.5V)
10uF Cap. (ByPass Cap.)
33ohm Res (For sensor)

#Add a led to pin d13 for check communication.


The energy supply of the arduino by 4x1.5V battery.
